# Safety Guardrails

## Protected files (do not modify without explicit user permission)

- `.env*`
- `package-lock.json` (use npm commands)
- `.github/workflows/` (CI)
- `prisma/migrations/` (use prisma migrate if used)

## Confirm with user first

- Database schema / collection shape changes
- Deleting files or directories
- Authentication or authorization behavior changes
- Breaking API response format changes

## Security

- Never log passwords, tokens, or PII
- Sanitize user input before database queries
